A towering corporate pyramid structure made of translucent glass and chrome, viewed from a dramatic low angle in a neon-lit cyberpunk cityscape. Each ascending level of the pyramid contains silhouetted figures in increasingly exaggerated, theatrical poses - the bottom level shows hunched workers, middle tiers feature figures with rigid robotic stances and oversized clipboards, while near the apex, figures strike grandiose dramatic poses with arms spread wide like performers on a stage. The pyramid glows with different colored neon lights at each level - cool blue at the base transitioning through purple to hot pink at the top. Rain streaks down the glass surfaces, reflecting the chaotic holographic advertisements floating in the misty background. The entire scene has a satirical, theatrical quality, suggesting corporate hierarchy as elaborate performance art.
